RESOURCE.STRING: Power Generation Tuning Test

This test is used to trim certain parameters while the engine is running. After all the desired values are set and the test is stopped the values can be permanently set in the ECM and will only require a single engine shutdown.

Initial Conditions
1. None
Steps
1. Select Start
2. Make desired changes
3. Select Apply
4. Select Stop
5. Select Yes to permanently save changes
Additional Information
1. All changes made during the test will be temporary until the test is stopped and the option to permanently save changes is selected
2. Changes made during the test will be reflected by the monitor parameters.
